        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">President Zelenskyy reported over <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #4D3060; color: black;" href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-21-04-2025-h1-1-2000-violations?source=website" target="_blank">2,000 violations</a> during the Easter ceasefire. The 30-hour ceasefire, proposed by Russia, was met with alleged reciprocal attacks as Russia and Ukraine accused each other of breaching it.<p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;filter:blur(5px);">
        The Russian defense ministry said that Ukraine shelled 444 bullets and carried out 900 drone strikes on its positions in Ukraine's eastern Donetsk region. Meanwhile, Zelenskyy dismissed the ceasefire as a fake PR exercise to appease the US.</p>
  
